name: tools_version
description: Set the justdown version everywhere at once — sync the cliVersion constant to one MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH value. Use when the user asks to bump the version before a release.
kind: tool
tags: [version, bump, release, manifest, go]
use_when: [bump the version, set the version, sync all versions, update version everywhere, make versions match]
